'''2021年世界男子手球錦標賽'''為第27屆[[世界男子手球錦標賽|世界男子手球錦標賽]]，是一項由[[國際手球總會|國際手球總會]]（IHF）主辦的全球性[[手球|手球]]賽事，於2021年1月13日至31日在埃及舉辦<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/features/detail/handball-everything-you-need-to-know-world-mens-championship-egypt-2021/|title=Top things you need to know for the World Men's Handball Championship Egypt 2021|publisher=[[奧林匹克頻道|Olympic Channel]]|date=2021-01-01|accessdate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111160200/https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/features/detail/handball-everything-you-need-to-know-world-mens-championship-egypt-2021/|archivedate=2021-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是埃及第二次主办世界男子手球锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dailynewsegypt.com/2021/01/13/glory-awaits-egyptian-national-handball-team/|title=Glory awaits Egyptian national handball team|publisher=Daily News Egypt|date=2021-01-13|accessdate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113140626/https://dailynewsegypt.com/2021/01/13/glory-awaits-egyptian-national-handball-team/|archivedate=2021-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该届比赛的参赛球队数为32支，与上届相比增加8支<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.ihf.info/en-us/mediacentre/news/newsdetails.aspx?ID=6215|title=IHF Council decides to increase number of teams at World Championships|date=2018-10-19|accessdate=2021-01-25|work=IHF|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915024004/https://archive.ihf.info/en-us/mediacentre/news/newsdetails.aspx?ID=6215|archivedate=2020-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管2021年1月时，全球仍受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]困扰，该届比赛仍旧按计划开赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arabnews.com/node/1791561/sport|title=Egypt defies pandemic to hold world handball tourney|publisher=Arab News|date=2021-01-13|accessdate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113010018/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1791561/sport|archivedate=2021-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为防止感染扩大，赛事主办方出台了相应的措施，包括[[无观众比赛|取消现场观众]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ihf.info/media-center/news/egypt-2021-world-championship-be-staged-without-spectators|title=Egypt 2021 – World Championship to be staged without spectators|work=IHF|date=2021-01-10|accessdate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110191154/https://www.ihf.info/media-center/news/egypt-2021-world-championship-be-staged-without-spectators|archivedate=2021-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>、强制相关人员在规定场合下佩戴口罩、定期对相关人员进行[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ihf.info/sites/default/files/2020-12/Egypt%202019%20COVID-19%20Medical%20Precaution%20Plan_Edition%202%20December%202020.pdf|title=COVID-19 Medical Precaution Plan Egypt 2021|work=IHF|date=2020-12-02|accessdate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121035411/https://www.ihf.info/sites/default/files/2020-12/Egypt%202019%20COVID-19%20Medical%20Precaution%20Plan_Edition%202%20December%202020.pdf|archivedate=2021-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

丹麦队在决赛中以26比24险胜瑞典队，成功卫冕。西班牙队在三四名决赛中以35比29击败法国，夺得季军。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/jan/31/denmark-retains-mens-handball-world-title-ahead-of/|title=Denmark retains men's handball world title ahead of Olympics|publisher=The Washington Times|date=2021-01-31|accessdate=2021-02-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201153940/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/jan/31/denmark-retains-mens-handball-world-title-ahead-of/|archivedate=2021-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

